== Espresso components ==

These packages make up the Espresso live installer.

 * espresso
 * espresso-frontend-gtk
 * espresso-ubuntu-artwork
 * espresso-ubuntu-doc
 * cdebconf # experimental, may be used or removed depending on testing

Espresso also needs to have some packages pre-installed on the live filesystem so that they can be installed on the target system without recourse to the network.

 * grub
 * yaboot

== NetworkManager ==

 * network-manager
 * nm-applet
